
DESCRIPTION:
^^^^^^^^^^^^

Text frame with "reflex" effect
Many properties can be set in "Property Editor" of Qt Designer
Custom widget plugin for Qt Designer


INSTALLATION:
^^^^^^^^^^^^^

qmake
make
make install (as root, install the librelfexplug.so in /usr/lib/qtX/plugins/designer)
verify the $LD_LIBRAY_PATH


TEST:
^^^^^

cd /test
qmake
make
in /bin directory the test program


DEVELOP:
^^^^^

cd /develop
qmake
make
in /bin directory the develop program



HARDWARE/SOFTWARE:
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

Build on Linux (ArchLinux) with Qt4 library and QDevelop


